    <center><table class="itemDisplayTable">
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Title:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Sales Improvemant Planing and Process of J.M.S.Store Ltd</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Authors:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Ratan Kumar Das</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Keywords:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Sales Improvemant Planing</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Issue Date:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">1-May-2010 </td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Publisher:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">SRM University</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Series/Report no.:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">P4923</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Abstract:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">This report is to describe the project that is based on SALESS IMPROVEMENT PLANNING AND PROCESS OF J.M.A. STORES LTD. A commercial Vehicle Dealer. On 1968 J.M.A. STORES LTD.had started sales of TATA Motors commercial Vehicle at dhanbad it is an authorized Dealer of commercial vehicle.The mission of this training is to provide actual reason of decline sales of TATA magic and find the process to improve the sales of
TATA DI RX. , TATA MAGIC AND TATA ACE. Increase the awareness level of the costumer and increase the business opportunity. A project is a study or research carried out by one that is carefully organized and designed to achieve a particular purpose and present the result. This is an Organization Study about J.M.A. STORES LTD.with real situation in organization .This enables me to get knowledge about the
functional and managerial activities of the concern. Since MBA is meant to study some field experience it is necessary to do this type of study. When I entered in to J.M.A.STORES LTD. At dhanbad branch I found that there were many departments like sales, finance, service, and workshop. It was very difficult to get the knowledge of all departments in two month so I
entered in sales department to get practical knowledge about the sales activities in an organization. , J.M.A.STORES.LTD Failed
Even having a good Brand image of TATA Motors
to achieve the organizational goal to sales the Tata new product TATA MAGIC. The senior manager of J.M.A. STORES LTD.mr R. K. Choudhary gave me one assignment to find out the actual reason of declining sales of the TATA
MAGIC At DHANBAD. I did my Assignment given by the senior manager and find out the actual reason of declining sales of TATA MAGIC.. For the purpose of my assignment, I apply open survey method and questioner method to understand the actual reason of low sales of TATA
MAGIC. For the purpose of survey I targeted TATA customer as well as their competitor Mahindra customer and PIGIO CUSTOMER. At first I set a question format to know the awareness level of customer about the product TATA MAGIC. And their features. And also I have done he comparative study of TATA MAGIC and their competitive product
tMahindra ape. And PIGIO passenger van.</td></tr>
